para_trans: Administrative budget for construction of Government Hostel for Backward Classes Girls, Jellarod, G. Ratnagiri
Department of Social Justice and Special Assistance
Government Memorandum No: BCH-2025 / Q.No.19 / Constructions
Madam Kama Marg, Martyr Rajguru Chowk,
Reference: - Department of Social Justice and Special Assistance, Government Decision No. BCH-2025 / Q. 124 / Constructions,

The Government Hostel for Backward Class Girls, Jail Road, Ratnagiri District under the Social Justice and Special Assistance Department has been constructed at a cost of Rs. 13.53 Rs. / - The Government decided to refer to the construction budget. Subject to the conditions prescribed under 01.07.2025, the Administrator has granted approval; the Government decision includes condition number (s) as follows: -
The operational mechanism for the present construction will be Maharashtra-State Infrastructure Development Corporation (MSIDC), Mumbai.
(2) The other provisions of the Government Decision shall remain in force.
The Government Corrigendum is available on the Government of Maharashtra website www.maharashtra.gov.in.
